title: Pixel Imprint register all inputs
content:
I am trying to register a finger on an imprint - but the imprint just continues when I used another finger (8 times for registering a fingerprint, and another finger accidentally on the sensor continued the register.

Any explanation for Pixel 4a to accept all fingerprint reads when registering a fingerprint, even when it seemed unrelated. In other cases, I see phones will outright reject that register.
